name: Metamaterial Hologram (🔮Generative Trippy Crystal)
description:
Look into the future through the generative trippy crystals.
"Metamaterial Hologram" from The "Generative Trippy Crystal" Collection by Hhvmid.

12 fps
Loop Video 
1080*1080 

"Metamaterial Hologram" is a video loop made with architectural landscapes and exaggerated color palettes mixed with mathematical algorithm scripts and a Pseudo random number generator (PRNG) to replicate a divination crystal ball.
